oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Proceedings of the Twenty-Second Annual Conference (1989). Social Events and Annual Membership Luncheon Meeting
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Bovine Practitioners, American Association of
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Have fun and enjoy yourself in Kansas City! Re-new old acquaintances, and make new ones, enjoy the camaraderie of colleagues and absorb the culture and character of the host city - these are the traditions of AABP meetings. Dr. Keith Sterner presided over the annual membership meeting and luncheon at the Allis Plaza on Friday, November 17. Director plaques were presented to outgoing directors David McClary, Richard Shirbroun and Kenneth Leslie. Treasurer Roland Jeans presented the treasurer's report.
